  "prompt": "Where can I buy raw egg noodles/ramen in Manipal? Is there a brand?",
  "response": "In Manipal, you can find raw egg noodles or ramen in various stores that stock Asian or international food items. Here are some places you can check:\n\n1. **Local Supermarkets**:\n   - **Foodland Supermarket**: Located in Manipal, it often carries a variety of Asian food products, including noodles and ramen.\n   - **More Supermarket**: Known for its wide range of groceries, it might have raw egg noodles or ramen in the international or noodles section.\n\n2. **Specialty Stores**:\n   Look for stores that specialize in Asian or imported goods. Sometimes, smaller grocery stores in the main market area might also carry these products.\n\n3. **Online Platforms**:\n   - **Amazon India**: You can search for raw egg noodles or ramen from brands like Ching\u2019s Secret, Maggi, or Nissin.\n   - **BigBasket**: Offers a variety of noodles and ramen, including those with eggs as an ingredient.\n\n4. **Brands to Look For**:\n   - **Ching\u2019s Secret**: Known for their range of noodles and instant foods.\n   - **Nissin**: Famous for their Cup Noodles and other ramen products.\n   - **Maggi**: While typically known for instant noodles, they might have specialty products.\n\nMake sure to check the packaging to confirm if the noodles contain egg, as some brands may have both egg-based and egg-free options. If you have specific dietary preferences or restrictions, reading the ingredients list is always a good idea.",
